'''Microsoft Word Viewer'''是一個可以在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]執行的[[免費軟體|免費軟體]]，並且可以檢視和列印[[Microsoft_Word|Microsoft Word]]的文件。這個軟體可以從[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]網站上免費下載。<ref name="obtain">{{Cite web|title = How to obtain the latest Word Viewer|url = http://support.microsoft.com/kb/891090|work = Support|publisher = Microsoft|date = 27 November 2012|accessdate = 31 March 2013|archive-date = 2020-12-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201215005902/https://support.microsoft.com/kb/891090|dead-url = no}}</ref> Word Viewer可以從被開啟的Word文件中複製其內容，然後在[[Word|Word]]文件內貼上。<ref name="obtain 97-2000">{{Cite web|url = http://support.microsoft.com/kb/165908|title = Description of the Microsoft Word Viewer 97-2000|work = Support|publisher = Microsoft|date = 19 January 2007|accessdate = 31 March 2013|archive-date = 2014-04-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140419082404/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/165908|dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 支援的格式 ==
Microsoft Word Viewer支援下列的格式：
* [[DOC格式|DOC格式]] (.doc)
* [[Office_Open_XML|Office Open XML]]文件 (.docx, .docm)
* [[RTF|RTF]]格式 (.rtf)
* [[文本文件|文本文件]] (.txt)
* [[HTML|HTML]] (.htm, .html) and [[MHTML|MHTML]] (.mht, .mhtml)
* [[Microsoft_Office_XML_formats|Word XML]]格式(.xml)
* [[WordPerfect|WordPerfect]] v5.x 和 v6.x 檔案 (.wpd)
* [[Microsoft_Works|Microsoft Works]] 文件 (.wps)
要檢視Office Open XML文件或安裝''Microsoft Office Word、Excel 及 PowerPoint 檔案格式相容性套件'' Microsoft Word Viewer就會被安裝。<ref name="obtain"/>

== 歷史 ==
在1999年3月17日發行的Word Viewer 97-2000可以開啟Word 97、Word 2000或Word for Mac 4.x或更高版本所建立的文件。<ref>{{cite web|title = Microsoft Word Viewer|url = http://www.theiet.org/help/software/wordviewer.cfm|work = Helper applications|publisher = [[The_Institution_of_Engineering_and_Technology|The Institution of Engineering and Technology]]|accessdate = 31 March 2013|date = 20 October 2011|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150907141700/http://www.theiet.org/help/software/wordviewer.cfm|archive-date = 2015-09-07|dead-url = yes}}</ref> 這個版本可以在Windows 16 位元或32 位元的[[Internet_Explorer|Internet Explorer]] 3.x 或更高版本上檢視Word文件。<ref name="obtain 97-2000"/>

Word Viewer 2003在2004年12月15日發行。它增加了Word XP和Word 2003早期版本的支援。

Word Viewer v11在2007年9月26日發行。本版本被包含在''Microsoft Office Word、Excel 及 PowerPoint 檔案格式相容性套件，''而且支援 Word 2007或更高版本的[[Office_Open_XML|Office Open XML]]文件格式。<ref name="Download page">{{Cite web|url = http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=4|title = Word Viewer|work = Download Center|publisher = Microsoft|date = 26 September 2007|accessdate = 31 March 2013|archive-date = 2017-11-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171130204715/https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=4|dead-url = no}}</ref> 從此以後Word Viewer的開發就停止了，所以在此期間，Microsot公司已經提供了其他閱讀Office文件的方式，例如：[[Office_Online|Office Online]]或[[WordPad|WordPad]]（內建在Windows的軟體），WordPad在Windows 7或更高版本中可以建立、查看和編輯Office Open XML文件（.DOCX），而且還支援RTF格式（.rtf）和文本文件格式（.txt）。<ref>{{cite web|title = Windows 7: The Top 10 Hidden Features|url = http://www.pcmag.com/slideshow_viewer/0,3253,l=255105&a=255105&po=3,00.asp|work = [[PC_Magazine|PC Magazine]]|publisher = [[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|accessdate = 3 April 2013|date = 30 September 2010|archive-date = 2016-04-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160408012832/http://www.pcmag.com/slideshow_viewer/0%2C3253%2Cl%3D255105%26a%3D255105%26po%3D3%2C00.asp|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title = Using WordPad|url = http://windows.microsoft.com/en-US/windows7/Using-WordPad|work = Windows portal|publisher = Microsoft|accessdate = 3 April 2013|archive-date = 2013-03-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130328213616/http://windows.microsoft.com/en-US/windows7/Using-WordPad|dead-url = no}}</ref>

Word Viewer沒有可在[[Windows|Windows]]以外系統執行的版本。

